values:
---Weekend
this wknd was pretty boring..friday i didnt do much, saturday me kayla 'n bri went to the mall to get kaylas present mwhahhah then later tht i nite just kinda chilled with some cool kids and had some fun8-) haha saturday me 'n kayla were suppose to go to a movie..but we couldn't find a ride so we ended up just gettin culvers:( it was all good tho:) haha

---Today
i was home sick today.. it was SO boring i just slept 'n watched tv:-D mwhahhaa my dad went to the store 'n got me a malt cup  man i love those things!! hehe but i guess we got alot of h/w:( er i really dont wanna do it! 



=-o

2day me 'n bri are gonna go to east towne to go get kayla's birthday presend:) mwhahhaha she'll never guess what were gonna get her:-P bri's gettin her hot spandex and prlly her hair dye!! wooo GO BRI!:-D I'm probably gonna get my strawberries 'n cream frappucino8-) those things r so GOOD!! hehe kaylas birthday is in 14 days!!! u all best be gettin her something.. ik i am:) 





14 DAYS!:-P woo

me 'n bri were  nerds 'n went to the library after our yearbook meeting and looked at books there for english, .. she found a book called "what my mother doesnt know" and i foudn the mistfits but i didnt really like it and i looked at bris book and i decided i liked it so we found another one and we both checked 'em out.. then we were REAL nerds by sitting AT the library READING our BOOKS!!! ahh it was quite scary.. but i "enjoy" reading now! ah make it stop:-[ hehe it was quite a scary nite

i just got finishing my book for english and it was kinda sad it made me relize some stuff:-/ haha 

wut do u do when you kno you need to get over someone because they don't like you and u kno they wont ever like u like tht again?.. but you just can't quite get over them... theres always somethings tht keeps reminding u of them and makes u like them again..and its hard when hes the only one thts ever liked me like tht and made me feel happy and tht i made a difference..to somebody.. but now tht theres nobody tht likes me tht i just don't feel happy or tht im quite needed to ne one.. 

sometimes being alone can just tear you up and make you feel like shit..



--i dont wish to be everything to everyone,
--i just wish to be something.. to someone



-**my world is crashing apart more and more each day**-

Today was beyond boring and i was SO tired! it was jareds birthday today(happy birthday jared) and he kinda got mad tht no one decorated his locker so i put a magnet on his locker so he'd feel better but he didnt like it:'( oh and mr. mathews picked some wrestling managers and guess who they are! ..Amanda wanted us to have vball prac. on friday morning so we wouldnt suck so much on mondays since we don't have prac. for 4 fuckin days in a row and the other team has vball prac. almost all week:-/ 2morrows vball pics :( most ppl went to the highskool vball game after prac. today..i would've but then i wouldnt have had a ride home:-/ 

now im off to practice my cheerleading.. we gotta prac. the cheer,dance, and routin 50 times each before the next prac. which is in 2 weeks.. we got our skirts there so HOT!:-D i love 'em

our vball games didn't exactly turn out tht great:-/ both A and B teams lost all 4 so we lsot all 8 of our games!:( after the game amandas mom took..amanda kayla brittnay bri and me to culvers and we saw victoria s. and ashlee there so we all chilled an ate our culvers8-) it was pretty fun:-P then i got home 'n just did my gay 'ol math homework:(

Well, everybody hurts sometimes,

Hold on, hold on, hold on, hold on, hold on, hold on
Everybody hurts. You are not alone

Today me 'n kayla biked over to Arbys:-P ya cuz we're cool kids like tht.. then she thought the guy at the counter was hott .. o man i thought he was UGLY! haha he had his pants pulled up past his belly button with his shirt tucked in all the way=-o:-/ haha then we just biked over to kaylas after and chilled now i have cheerleading at 5:30 and we get our uniforms!!! ahh there gonna be so HOTT:-* hehe

me 'n kayla went to the mall and went shoppin for awhile and i got new hair dye and nail polish:) mwhahah we saw a REALLY hott guy tht looked like our age at the mall:-* o la la then once i went home i dyed my hair:) it didn't turn out THT good but it still looks hott but im gonna re-do it 2morrow:-P hehe then i painted my nails some sparkly dark redish color its quite hott! then i just sat here and kinda just listened to some tunes8-) keepin it cool ;-)

sarah kristin bri and kayla came over after skool to get ready to go to the parade 'n game when all the sudden sarah grabs some cool sparkly sunglasses and is like "dude i am so gonna wear these there!" were all like.."DO IT!" so then i decided to wear my awesum new years hat tht me 'n kayla got 2 years ago.. so we're walking there and thts when i decided i was the pimp 'n kayla bri 'n of course sarah were my hoes:) it was quite fun being the pimp ..(every now and then i eliminated ppl for being bad hoes;-), but i still love em!:) ) once we were watching the ftball game me kayla and patrick were watching ashley hornbeck or w/e and travis reigstad make out and crap..man those kids were all over eachother=-o:-/ haha then whne they were kissing travis looked over and saw us looking at him so we all kinda laughed (aw poor them we ruined there romantic kiss;-) hehe) oppsy ..Finally once the game was over we were walking over to pick 'n save when all the sudden these highskoolers moon us! so were like "UR GUYSES ASSES R REALLY WHITE!!!" and there like"well we dont go tanning!" so then we said "well maybe you should!" then we started talking to them and i found out they were in my brothers grade=-o and he said my bro was pretty cool im like no he isn't.. hes a nerd wut r u talking about.. hahah g/ts
then when we were in pick 'n save.. oh man we were HUGE men ..kristins grabbing everything she can almost and she only has like $4 hahaha i jsut got a donut b/c im poor like tht and only had a $1 with me:) 
once we got back to my house.. we pigged out and watched OLD SKOOL hell yea hehe 

tht was a fun nite girls!! love you all!!

Kayla Bri Brittnay Kristin and me we all went to the other teams vball games (b/c we hafta if there home games >:-[ ) it was pretty boring so we left after the first team was done.. we were walkin ova to kristins when kayla drops her cell phone when shes handing it to brittnay we all looked and there like screaming..(oh my kayla) then once we were there kristin coulndt quite find conditioner oh gosh..once we had the kool-aid in after awhile it started turning green so like almost everyone sittin there freaking out, kayla 'n britt go wash theres out.. man wut a fun time. then kayla randomly wants to decide to get her hair cut so she makes bri do it and so britt 'n kristin come join.. i just sat and watched(im not good with cutting hair:-/ lol)


don't ever trust kool-aid again :( haha

woo rite now im paintin my nails purple.. you gotta have some NORSKIE SPIRIT for homecoming:-P hell ya! today was beyond boring! for vball prac. we got to go prac. with the Varsity girls..tht was pretty fun i learned quite a bit of stuff from them:-P hehe i think i like somebody new=-o but who knows maybe not..

Today was pretty boring, in tech we started our mirrors!! =-o oh man tht was scary lol In spanish we picked our spanish names and Heidi took margarita and i was really mad!>:( So instead i picked pepita? haha wut a wierd name:( haha Once volleyball started.. oh man:( we had to prac. with ppl but i guess i just kinda practiced by myself cuz no one wanted to prac. with me:-/:( then the A teams and B teams split into halfs so there a "A-gold" and "A-purple" and "B gold" and "B purple" its so gay cuz we dont even go to all the games..:( haha but least im on a team with all my friends:-P i haven't quite found out who i like:(

today was a very strange day, in gym 3rd hour mrs skripka(however you spell it) came and took me outta gym to the office then i talked with her about some stuff and i thought i was in trouble but lucky me i wasnt:) but then in the hall mr. parker makes me stand by him as if im in trouble:( and just randomly starts talking to me bout some stuff like.. "did you kno your hair is pink?" and im like"yes i did kno tht" he said"did you get it professionally done or did you do it?" me"umm i did it?" haha then he said "are you in a band?" me "no" him "do  you play an instrument?" me "no" him "well, i think you should play the  bass guitar" me "um ok?" ..it was a very random conversation yet again mr. parker is very RaNdOm hehe then vball prac. kidna sucked cuz i wasnt on the A team rite away so i was kinda donw bout tht then the end of practice came and i was kinda nervous to find out if i was on the A team or not and i ended up makin it..it was such a relief:) lol ya tht was my day.. pretty boring eh?

today in skool, it was pretty boring..i think english is the most fun class its wierd but i kinda like expressing my feelings:-/ In volleyball they were picking some people to be on the A team so we all kinda tried a lil harder.. i think i'm gonna make the B team 'n i really don't want to:( its seems like everyones just better than me:-/ maybe volleyball just isn't the right sport for me? im just no so sure..



i (hate) skool

sometimes don't you just wish you could get away just for one day? leave all your problems behind 'n see wut its like to be happy? ik i wish i could:( i try my hardest to get you to notice me but sometimes tht just doesnt work, you just seem to notice her:-/ i guess i just gotta take the truth 'n find it out the hard way tht sometimes ppl just won't like you for who you are:(


i w.i.s.h i could get a.w.a.y!

Well after the movie she left 'n i just chilled here and my brother yelled at me for having icecream for dinner but i just ignored him :) hehe
